;重写pclogo时代的设置数组指令
;命令版本号v1.4

to hair.old.aset :a :v :c
hair.detect
if and (not word? :a) (not array? :a) [hair.debug.error "设置数组语法错误 stop]
if and list? :v 1=count :v [make "v first :v]
if word? :a [make "a thing :a]
ifelse list? :v [mdsetitem map [? + 1] :v :a :c][setitem :v+1 :a :c]
end
bury "hair.old.aset
